WINTER 2018
Jon and Vinny DELTA ONE CHEFS
Jon Shook and Vinny Dotolo are two of Los Angeles' most acclaimed chefs
and restaurateurs and now the newest additions to Delta's culinary team.
Their menu for Delta One features dishes inspired by many of the must-have
offerings at their local hot spots, including James Beard Award winning
Animal, Son of a Gun and Jon & Vinny's. Shook and Dotolo are known for
wowing guests at their restaurants trougn arverse onerings and tamillar
flavors presented in bold, unexpected ways. In keeping with Delta's ethos of
using local, fresh and seasonal ingredients, the LA duo's onboard menus are
sourced from area farmers and purveyors.
SETTLING IN
Signature Cocktail *
Enjoy our signature Delta Sunrise Cocktail featuring bombay sapphire gin
with cranberry-apple juice and a splash of ginger ale
Honey Black Pepper Walnuts
STARTERS
Prosciutto with Marinated Mozzarella
Garden of Farm Gem Lettuce Salad
with Calabrian caesar dressing, parmesan and breadcrumbs
Charred Onion Soup
with gruyere croutons
Assorted Warm Breads
MAIN COURSE
Delta offers a 'Dine and Rest' option in which your meal will be
delivered at once, as a single service. Please inform your flight attendant
if you prefer this option when making your entrée selection.
Please select one of the options below
